snippet.title: Furwind Launch Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Furwind is a colorful, pixel art style, action-platformer game that evokes the challeging classics of the old days. Embark on this epic adventure in which a litle fox will fight the ominous darkness that is invading its world. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/881750/Furwind/

Itch.io: https://boomfire-games.itch.io/furwind


· Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Boomfiregames/ 
· Twitter: https://twitter.com/BoomfireGames 
· Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/boomfiregames/ 
· Web: http://www.boomfiregames.com/
